Title: Sparks of Life: The Waking Shores
Description:
Cannae ya smell the sweet scent of adventure on the wind?

The Waking Shores are close ta bursting with energy and life right now. Get out there and claim a piece for yourself!
ObjectivesText: Collect 100 Sparks of Life in the Waking Shores, while in War Mode.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak with Fieldmaster Emberath in Valdrakken.
